snippet: French champions Paris St Germain plunged further into crisis when they were beaten 2-1 at En Avant Guingamp in Ligue 1 on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: French champions Paris St Germain plunged further into crisis when they were beaten 2-1 at En Avant Guingamp in Ligue 1 on Saturday.

headline.main: PSG Thrown Deeper Into Crisis by Guingamp Defeat
